---
// About Us Component
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 via-orange-50 to-yellow-50 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-orange-300 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-40 right-20 w-24 h-24 bg-teal-300 rounded-full animate-bounce"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-1/4 w-20 h-20 bg-orange-400 rounded-full animate-ping"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <!-- Header with enhanced animation -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-full mb-6 animate-bounce">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-teal-800 mb-4 animate-slide-up">
        Sobre Nosotros
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-orange-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto animate-slide-up-delay">
        Somos una organización comprometida con el desarrollo espiritual y la transformación de vidas
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission & Vision with enhanced cards -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
      <!-- Mission -->
      <div class="group bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-orange-200 hover:border-orange-400 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-800 group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Nuestra Misión</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Llevar la palabra de Dios a todas las personas, inspirando fe, esperanza y amor. 
          Nos dedicamos a crear comunidades unidas en Cristo, fomentando el crecimiento espiritual 
          y el servicio a los demás.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Vision -->
      <div class="group bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-teal-200 hover:border-teal-400 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-800 group-hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">Nuestra Visión</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Ser una luz en el mundo, transformando vidas a través del amor de Cristo. 
          Aspiramos a ser una comunidad que refleje los valores del Reino de Dios, 
          impactando positivamente en la sociedad.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- History with timeline animation -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl mb-20 border border-orange-200 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-teal-400"></div>
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-teal-400 rounded-full mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-teal-800 mb-4">Nuestra Historia</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-orange-600">Un viaje de fe y crecimiento</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="group text-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:animate-pulse">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2018</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-3">Fundación</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Nacimos con el propósito de servir a Dios y a la comunidad</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group text-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-teal-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:animate-pulse">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2020</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-3">Crecimiento</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Expandimos nuestros ministerios y alcance comunitario</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group text-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:animate-pulse">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2024</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-3">Innovación</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Incorporamos tecnología para llegar a más personas</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Team with enhanced cards -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-teal-600 rounded-full mb-6">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-teal-800 mb-4">Nuestro Equipo</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-orange-600">Conoce a las personas que hacen posible nuestra misión</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Team Member 1 -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 text-center border border-orange-200 hover:border-orange-400 transform hover:-translate-y-4">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 via-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 relative">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">JP</span>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Juan Pérez</h3>
          <p class="text-orange-600 font-medium mb-4 text-lg">Pastor Principal</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Líder espiritual con más de 15 años de experiencia en ministerio</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-orange-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-teal-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Member 2 -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 text-center border border-teal-200 hover:border-teal-400 transform hover:-translate-y-4">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-400 via-teal-500 to-teal-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 relative">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">MG</span>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-400 to-teal-600 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">María González</h3>
          <p class="text-teal-600 font-medium mb-4 text-lg">Directora de Ministerio</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Especialista en desarrollo de programas comunitarios</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-teal-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-orange-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Member 3 -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 text-center border border-orange-200 hover:border-orange-400 transform hover:-translate-y-4 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 via-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 relative">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">CR</span>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Carlos Rodríguez</h3>
          <p class="text-orange-600 font-medium mb-4 text-lg">Coordinador de Jóvenes</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Apasionado por el ministerio juvenil y el discipulado</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-orange-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-teal-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact with enhanced design -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-teal-200 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-orange-400"></div>
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-orange-400 rounded-full mb-6">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-teal-800 mb-4">Contáctanos</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-orange-600">Estamos aquí para servirte</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Contact Info -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="group flex items-center p-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-teal-800 text-lg">Dirección</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Calle Principal 123, Ciudad</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group flex items-center p-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-teal-50 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-teal-800 text-lg">Teléfono</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">+1 (555) 123-4567</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group flex items-center p-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-teal-800 text-lg">Email</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">info@chaskisum.com</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="group">
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-teal-800 mb-3">Nombre</label>
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <input type="text" class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-orange-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-300" placeholder="Tu nombre">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="group">
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-teal-800 mb-3">Email</label>
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <input type="email" class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-orange-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-300" placeholder="tu@email.com">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="group">
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-teal-800 mb-3">Mensaje</label>
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="absolute top-3 left-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <textarea rows="4" class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-orange-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-300" placeholder="¿En qué podemos ayudarte?"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-600 text-white py-4 px-8 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:from-orange-500 hover:to-orange-700 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Enviar Mensaje</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  
  @keyframes slide-up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fade-in 0.8s ease-out;
  }
  
  .animate-slide-up {
    animation: slide-up 0.8s ease-out;
  }
  
  .animate-slide-up-delay {
    animation: slide-up 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }
</style>
